<td>-</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>0.16</td>
<td>Connect to local DB (same <code>DATABASE_URL</code> if one shared DB, OR own <code>sunpor_dev</code> on your machine)</td>
<td>0.6</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>0.17</td>
<td>Review <code>SignalExport.xlsx</code> and <code>signal_catalog_seed.csv</code></td>
<td>- (start Day 1)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>0.18</td>
<td>Verify factors, units, datatypes for all 104 signals</td>
<td>-</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>0.19</td>
<td>Write signal mapping notes (tag -&gt; group -&gt; area -&gt; factor)</td>
<td>-</td>
</tr>
<tr>
