<td>Test DB connection with a simple script or <code>psql</code></td>
<td>0.11</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>0.21</td>
<td>Import seed into local <code>signal_catalog</code> (script or SQL)</td>
<td>0.11</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p><strong>Local setup options (pick one for the team):</strong></p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Option</th>
<th>Best for</th>
<th>How</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><strong>A - Shared local DB</strong></td>
<td>Same office / one machine hosts DB</td>
<td>Person 1 runs Postgres; Person 2 uses <code>host:5432</code> on LAN IP</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>B - Each own DB</strong></td>
<td>Remote team / work offline</td>
<td>Each developer has own <code>sunpor_dev</code>; sync via migrations + seed files</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
